How to use word "have" in French

1) "I/je"
   When using "i" in French,"je" will be "j'ai"
   *Example : J'ai trois oranges ,J'ai dix-sept ans
2) "You/tu"
   "you" in French will get additional "as"
   *Example : Tu as deux maisons ,Tu as un croissant
3) "He,she/il,elle"
   When using "He or she" will get additional "a"
   *Example : il a un fils ,elle a cinq pommes
4) "They/Ils,elles"
   When using "they" will get additional "ont"
   *Example : Ils ont deux voitures ,Elles ont trois chouettes
5) "We/nous"
   When using "we/nous", will get additional "avons" (also can use "on a" sometimes)
   *Example : Nous avons un voiture ,on a trois livre
